accessibility.text: The Fed disappeared money form the system by decreasing bank reserves
This is what the Fed does to fight inflation
Assume the Fed is presently holding 100b in Bonds
The Fed now holds 80b in Bonds
Fed sells 20b in bonds to the public
Public pays with checks drawn on their bank accounts
The Fed disappeared money form the system by decreasing bank reserves
This is what the Fed does to fight inflation
